            <p>Velocity and flow rate conversions are essential for fluid m=
echanics, traffic engineering, and environmental engineering applications. =
These conversions help engineers analyze fluid systems, design drainage inf=
rastructure, and specify pump requirements for various industrial and munic=
ipal applications.</p>
